2d78b62","parent":"> **このアプリの機能・要件**","children":[{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8196-85b3-d2b175d9a644","parent":"- **数字を表示する部分**（`ft.Text`コントロール）、**「プラス」ボタン**（`ft.FilledTonalButton`コントロール）、**「リセット」ボタン**（`ft.FilledTonalButton`コントロール）の3つで構成される。","children":[]},{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81be-9118-fee474011677","parent":"- 各コントロールの並べ方に特に指定はない（横並びでもいい）","children":[]},{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8188-a833-f128a7c81396","parent":"- 「プラス」ボタンをクリックすると、数字が１ずつ増える。","children":[]},{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8192-8a36-d78dc9562d24","parent":"- 「リセット」ボタンをクリックすると、数字が０に戻る。","children":[]}]},{"type":"toggle","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8159-9218-d3c42b6f2dcc","parent":"ヒント1","children":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-813d-8a6b-de6f1f6d25b6","parent":"各ボタンには`on_click`プロパティを設定する必要があります。","children":[]}]},{"type":"toggle","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81ed-9685-fd872f7653a1","parent":"ヒント2","children":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8129-9d5c-c37b16bb99d0","parent":"「プラス」ボタンの`on_click`には数字を増やす`plus_number`関数、「リセット」ボタンの`on_click`には数字を0にする`reset_number`関数を設定するといいでしょう","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-812b-a72b-f4b2aa84f9cf","parent":"（`plus_number`関数と`reset_number`関数は自作する）","children":[]}]},{"type":"toggle","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81ec-b267-e12d60e87e82","parent":"ヒント3","children":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-812e-89a3-ef1b65329ed2","parent":"`ft.Text`コントロールの表示内容を設定する`value`は文字列型です。そのため、`plus_number`関数の処理内容は少し工夫しなければなりません。","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8123-ad1d-dac915715c01","parent":"1. `ft.Text`コントロールの`value`を整数型に変換して他の変数（例：`num`）に格納","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8181-9b38-f9d94c972d6a","parent":"2. `num`を一つ増やす","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81c9-ac86-c7fb47c7c6d8","parent":"3. `num`を文字列型に変換して、`ft.Text`コントロールの`value`に格納","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81a9-9aff-c4ceac8bb332","parent":"4. `ft.Text`コントロールを`update`する","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-810d-b7c0-dd531e7b9858","parent":"※ファイルは「flet-prac3.py」として保存","children":[]},{"type":"heading_1","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8123-9c59-c3c31e4a10c9","parent":"# 進捗アンケート","children":[]},{"type":"divider","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81aa-aec8-dafb6a31221e","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81a6-83e4-f87d39d43b71","parent":"この問題が終了した人は、以下のGoogleフォームに回答してください。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8110-b2d6-f9f4ce7c5ad9","parent":"回答後、練習問題の回答例のURLをメールでお送りします。","children":[]},{"type":"quote","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-8163-a603-fbef7ad47608","parent":"> ","children":[{"type":"bookmark","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81e1-8616-f079aa45f2cf","parent":"[bookmark](https://forms.gle/FFBeAXNS5VA5AJV29)","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"17d2297f-7a72-81b9-a4c8-c72951bd4602","parent":"","children":[]}]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"前期","id":"/posts/course/前期/1"},{"title":"Flet","id":"/posts/post/flet-1"},{"title":"Fletの練習問題3 (1)","id":"/posts/post/flet-117d2297f-7a72-80f3-b72b-d2e514002c10"}],"parentTitle":"Flet","childNavs":[{"title":"0. GUIとFletについて (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-8052-85a5-e7de3049579f","child":true},{"title":"1. Fletのインストール (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80a2-b044-e17924cfa345","child":true},{"title":"2. カウンターを作ってみよう (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-803c-829b-ea2844416a5c","child":true},{"title":"3. ページの生成 (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80e6-8335-c5d7dabb7f09","child":true},{"title":"4. コントロール (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-807e-a215-e7557816fbdc","child":true},{"title":"Fletの練習問題1 (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80be-a21a-ef14a273a257","child":true},{"title":"5. コントロールのレイアウト (1)","id":"17d2297f-7a72-80b3-8ec3-dee35809a987","child":true},{"title":"F